7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Integrately and Notion Automations share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Conditional Logic, Templates. Where Integrately pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Api Connections and Scheduling and Webhook Support, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Notion Automations uniquely offers Team Collaboration and Ai Actions, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Integrately holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Notion Automations scores 5/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Integrately and Notion Automations offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Integrately's free tier and Notion Automations's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
